{"analysis_markdown_path":"articles/2026/06/03/itm_7eed37bd41712388/index.md","canonical_url":"https://openai.com/index/frontier-safety-blueprint/","category_id":"ai-safety","collected_at":"2026-06-06T14:15:18Z","content_hash":"b316b81f75a42ed11e75bced71fb319d63a130bcea6f59bf9b3281ba3f69d611","evidence":[{"label":"OpenAI article","type":"url","url":"https://openai.com/index/frontier-safety-blueprint/"},{"label":"Blueprint PDF","type":"url","url":"https://cdn.openai.com/pdf/25752ecb-0e5c-47f9-b9e4-c0f4d76f8d3d/a-blueprint-for-a-federal-framework.pdf"},{"label":"White House EO linked by OpenAI","type":"url","url":"https://www.whitehouse.gov/presidential-actions/2026/06/promoting-advanced-artificial-intelligence-innovation-and-security/"}],"external_id":"openai-frontier-safety-blueprint-2026-06-03","fetched_at":"2026-06-06T14:15:18Z","fingerprint":"7eed37bd417123881f21a6c7b10061d0ac8465ae2673ffddafdceb126fdb5be1","id":"itm_7eed37bd41712388","item_id":"itm_7eed37bd41712388","language":"zh-CN","published_at":"2026-06-03T00:00:00Z","reading_minutes":23,"score":93,"sort_at":"2026-06-03T00:00:00Z","source_id":"openai-frontier-safety-blueprint","source_name":"OpenAI Global Affairs","source_type":"report","summary_zh":"OpenAI 在 2026-06-03 发布 Frontier Safety Blueprint，主张美国应建立耐久的联邦 frontier AI safety framework。蓝图分为三段：通过 reverse federalism 把州级共识上收为国家框架；强化 CAISI 作为前沿 AI 评估、标准和第三方认证机构；动员 whole-of-government resilience plan 处理网络、CBRN、RSI、算力、政府采购和国际协作问题。","tags":["AI Safety","Frontier Governance","CAISI","RSI","Policy"],"title":"OpenAI Frontier Safety Blueprint：从公司安全声明转向联邦制度建设","title_hash":"5ec1df1fe2ce0213f6b1fb6311cd2accff7ece99679211b165a271ff2897c17b","type":"report","updated_at":"2026-06-03T00:00:00Z","url":"https://openai.com/index/frontier-safety-blueprint/"}
{"analysis_markdown_path":"articles/2026/06/02/itm_cad15834c2296176/index.md","canonical_url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.01166","category_id":"ai-safety","collected_at":"2026-06-06T15:09:37Z","content_hash":"48b99b297970dd3ddc7e9a7f6e26f5dd553cb57d355577046af107b94ebd0822","evidence":[{"label":"arXiv abstract page","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.01166"},{"label":"Hugging Face paper page","type":"url","url":"https://huggingface.co/papers/2606.01166"},{"label":"GitHub repository","type":"url","url":"https://github.com/Yunhao-Feng/BraveGuard"},{"label":"Hugging Face model page","type":"url","url":"https://huggingface.co/Yunhao-Feng/BraveGuard"},{"label":"AgentHazard project page","type":"url","url":"https://yunhao-feng.github.io/AgentHazard/"},{"label":"AIRGuard related paper","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2605.28914"},{"label":"WebAgentGuard related paper","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2604.12284"},{"label":"FATE related paper","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2605.11882"}],"external_id":"arxiv:2606.01166","fetched_at":"2026-06-06T15:09:37Z","fingerprint":"764622eef19dfde65207aa0cd8f1a1d6eaf62b62014163ea7b54ca0232914771","id":"itm_cad15834c2296176","item_id":"itm_cad15834c2296176","language":"zh-CN","published_at":"2026-06-02T05:59:47Z","reading_minutes":28,"score":94,"sort_at":"2026-06-02T05:59:47Z","source_id":"braveguard-agent-safety","source_name":"Hugging Face Papers / BraveGuard","source_type":"paper","summary_zh":"BraveGuard 是 2026-06-02 更新、Hugging Face 在 2026-06-04 提交的 computer-use agent 安全论文与开源 guard model。它把安全检测从 prompt/response 级别推进到 trajectory-level：先从公开威胁来源挖掘新风险，把风险合成为 7,308 个可执行 agent tasks，覆盖 28 类风险和 32 种攻击方法，再用 OpenClaw 等环境采集轨迹、标注安全标签和 rationale，训练 Llama-Guard-8B、Qwen3-Guard-8B、Qwen3-Guard-4B 等 guard backbones。README 报告在 AgentHazard-Strongest 上 Qwen3-Guard-8B 达到 83.65% accuracy、91.28% recall、89.22% F1，off-the-shelf guard 平均 accuracy 从 38.79% 提升到 82.38%；但在 ATBench-500 上并未全面超过 AgentDoG，data exfiltration 和 compliance bypass 仍是后续难点。本轮因本地代理/DNS 限制未能下载 PDF，正文明确以 arXiv、HF、GitHub README、模型页和 AgentHazard 背景页为证据边界。","tags":["AI Safety","Agent Safety","Computer Use","Guard Model","Trajectory Safety","AgentHazard"],"title":"BraveGuard: From Open-World Threats to Safer Computer-Use Agents","title_hash":"225597914a29788e031e18be5f217dcac6ec3d6097c91da377c1752426b0f708","type":"paper","updated_at":"2026-06-02T05:59:47Z","url":"https://huggingface.co/papers/2606.01166"}
{"analysis_markdown_path":"articles/2026/06/01/itm_2d450e628d639adc/index.md","canonical_url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.02031","category_id":"llm-agent","collected_at":"2026-06-06T14:15:18Z","content_hash":"196b74b7bfcecf8343440000aadce467cd67599c252793f870d087b91bf04309","evidence":[{"label":"Hugging Face paper page","type":"url","url":"https://huggingface.co/papers/2606.02031"},{"label":"arXiv page","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.02031"},{"label":"Project page","type":"url","url":"https://openwebrl.github.io"},{"label":"GitHub repository","type":"url","url":"https://github.com/OpenWebRL/OpenWebRL"},{"label":"Hugging Face organization","type":"url","url":"https://huggingface.co/OpenWebRL"}],"external_id":"arxiv:2606.02031","fetched_at":"2026-06-06T14:15:18Z","fingerprint":"2d450e628d639adc56a43c7aae50e5577ae92e918731b4c67b585587f9af875b","id":"itm_2d450e628d639adc","item_id":"itm_2d450e628d639adc","language":"zh-CN","published_at":"2026-06-01T00:00:00Z","reading_minutes":22,"score":94,"sort_at":"2026-06-02T00:00:00Z","source_id":"openwebrl","source_name":"Hugging Face Papers / OpenWebRL","source_type":"paper","summary_zh":"OpenWebRL 是 Microsoft 团队在 2026-06-01 发布的视觉网页 Agent 论文与开源框架。它把 live-browser infrastructure、少量监督初始化、多模态上下文管理、轨迹级成功判断和多轮 RL 优化放进同一条训练管线，用 0.4K 初始化轨迹和 2.2K 开放式 RL 任务训练 OpenWebRL-4B，在 Online-Mind2Web 与 DeepShop 上分别报告 67.0% 和 64.0% 成功率。","tags":["Agent","Web Agent","Online RL","Computer Use","Multimodal"],"title":"OpenWebRL：把视觉网页 Agent 的训练从离线轨迹推向真实网站在线强化学习","title_hash":"3e6071d665b2408a44ae9f44e73ba84e921a1e8de698951ceccb5131084450fb","type":"paper","updated_at":"2026-06-02T00:00:00Z","url":"https://huggingface.co/papers/2606.02031"}
{"analysis_markdown_path":"articles/2026/06/02/itm_fd9b87df1fe1b911/index.md","canonical_url":"https://www.anthropic.com/news/expanding-project-glasswing","category_id":"ai-safety","collected_at":"2026-06-06T15:02:28Z","content_hash":"12fff97bc82d2e96cceb32bcfc56b29fd50fd6c02de6b66229ddd4937b555ce6","evidence":[{"label":"Anthropic expansion post","type":"url","url":"https://www.anthropic.com/news/expanding-project-glasswing"},{"label":"Project Glasswing initial update","type":"url","url":"https://www.anthropic.com/research/glasswing-initial-update"},{"label":"CVD dashboard","type":"url","url":"https://red.anthropic.com/2026/cvd/"},{"label":"Claude Mythos Preview red-team writeup","type":"url","url":"https://red.anthropic.com/2026/mythos-preview/"},{"label":"Sandra Joyce testimony","type":"url","url":"https://homeland.house.gov/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/2026-06-04-CIP-AI-Hearing.pdf"}],"external_id":"anthropic-expanding-project-glasswing-2026-06-02","fetched_at":"2026-06-06T15:02:28Z","fingerprint":"fd9b87df1fe1b911c46c3add7cef05f95691d2206a057371114938d9714dca10","id":"itm_fd9b87df1fe1b911","item_id":"itm_fd9b87df1fe1b911","language":"zh-CN","published_at":"2026-06-02T00:00:00Z","reading_minutes":28,"score":95,"sort_at":"2026-06-02T00:00:00Z","source_id":"anthropic-project-glasswing-expansion","source_name":"Anthropic News / Frontier Red Team","source_type":"report","summary_zh":"Anthropic 2026-06-02 宣布扩展 Project Glasswing：在约 50 个初始伙伴基础上，新增约 150 个需满足安全要求的新组织，覆盖 15+ 国家以及电力、水务、医疗、通信、硬件等关键基础设施。文章的核心不是单纯扩大名单，而是承认 Mythos-class cyber 模型已把瓶颈从漏洞发现推向验证、披露、补丁设计和部署。配套初始更新显示，Project Glasswing 第一个月发现 10,000+ 被估为 high/critical 的漏洞；开源扫描中有 23,019 个候选、6,202 个 high/critical 估计、1,752 个经审查 high/critical 候选，其中 90.6% 为 true positive、62.4% 仍确认为 high/critical。CVD dashboard 截至 2026-05-22 显示 1,596 个已披露、97 个 upstream patched、88 个 advisories，说明真正稀缺的是人类 triage、维护者修复和部署吞吐。局限是大量漏洞仍在披露窗口内，数字多来自 Anthropic/合作方口径，不能把估计 high/critical、disclosed 和 patched 混为一谈。","tags":["AI Safety","Cybersecurity","Project Glasswing","Claude Mythos Preview","CVD"],"title":"Anthropic 扩展 Project Glasswing：从“AI 找漏洞”转向“AI 时代的验证、披露与补丁产能”","title_hash":"68958518357099abe99e120d2e5f3c0613949afd4e3bf3ab09444a1c6e74196f","type":"report","updated_at":"2026-06-02T00:00:00Z","url":"https://www.anthropic.com/news/expanding-project-glasswing"}
{"analysis_markdown_path":"articles/2026/06/01/itm_f9e47b7d4ea512dc/index.md","canonical_url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.02398","category_id":"llm-post-training","collected_at":"2026-06-06T14:53:28Z","content_hash":"402d37405631916c9a3aca391395bedf693c54ced93655f12783ce60b7106378","evidence":[{"label":"arXiv abstract page","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.02398"},{"label":"Hugging Face paper page","type":"url","url":"https://huggingface.co/papers/2606.02398"},{"label":"HyperAI PDF extraction page","type":"url","url":"https://hyper.ai/en/papers/2606.02398"},{"label":"Wolf Digest 2026-06-04","type":"url","url":"https://wolfdigest.com/"},{"label":"Hyperion Consulting weekly research decoded","type":"url","url":"https://hyperion-consulting.io/en/insights/ai-research-decoded-the-rise-of-specialized-reasoning-engines-in-physical-ai"}],"external_id":"arxiv:2606.02398","fetched_at":"2026-06-06T14:53:28Z","fingerprint":"8bbd3dd37fc6b9b6d218d5c16d6b530424444e5b5e6ee8b1a5e62aa40f7c8df7","id":"itm_f9e47b7d4ea512dc","item_id":"itm_f9e47b7d4ea512dc","language":"zh-CN","published_at":"2026-06-01T15:44:56Z","reading_minutes":31,"score":94,"sort_at":"2026-06-01T15:44:56Z","source_id":"local-perturbation-multidomain-rl","source_name":"Hugging Face Papers / arXiv","source_type":"paper","summary_zh":"这篇 2026-06-01 提交的论文研究 LLM 多领域 RL 后训练中的能力干扰：数学、代码、问答和创意写作各用 5,120 条样本训练 Qwen3-4B-Thinking-2507，作者发现单领域 RL 更新很稀疏，约 77% 到 89% 参数变化低于 1e-7 且 top 10% changed neurons 的平均 Jaccard overlap 低于 0.19，但领域间仍会通过共享活跃计算路径发生方向性冲突。论文用 local perturbation theory 把后续领域对早期领域的伤害写成二阶项，并投影到共享冲突子空间解释局部损伤；短 Re-Math refresh 可把 Code->Math->QA->CW 顺序后的 Math 从 57.66 恢复到 66.04，最佳平均分 66.39。局限是本轮未取得稳定原图 URL，完整训练超参、所有表格和 rollback 坐标构造仍需后续补读。","tags":["Post-Training","RL","Multi-Domain RL","Interference","Refresh"],"title":"多领域 RL 后训练的局部扰动理论：共享冲突子空间、二阶损伤与短 refresh 恢复","title_hash":"7f1a09583f9d2c5ddcb39054c368316538c826a473f584596e139c324578272f","type":"paper","updated_at":"2026-06-01T15:44:56Z","url":"https://huggingface.co/papers/2606.02398"}
